---
description: Repository-wide coding agent standards
alwaysApply: true
---

Before making changes, read `agent-instructions/AGENT.md`.

Follow all repository rules in `agent-instructions/`.

Key rules:

- Keep changes small and focused.
- Do not invent requirements.
- Do not refactor unrelated code.
- Add or update tests for behavior changes.
- Do not add dependencies unless justified.
- Do not weaken security.
- Run relevant checks.
- Report failures honestly.
- Use `agent-instructions/agent-response-format.md` in final responses.
